01:16.840 --> 01:22.840
The cottage is in the middle of a field. What can we do in the middle of a field?

01:22.840 --> 01:24.840
Why are we going there?

01:24.840 --> 01:26.840
asks Laura.

01:26.840 --> 01:29.840
Their dad is very tired.

01:29.840 --> 01:33.840
He says he wants to relax and to sleep a lot.

01:33.840 --> 01:38.840
Their mum loves the country. She wants to walk and paint.

01:38.840 --> 01:41.840
It's a very beautiful part of England.

01:41.840 --> 01:42.840
She says.

01:42.840 --> 01:46.840
Full of culture, tradition, mystery, mystery.

01:46.840 --> 01:48.840
