18:18.840 --> 18:20.840
Stonehenge.

18:20.840 --> 18:26.840
Stonehenge is a very old monument in the south of England.

18:26.840 --> 18:29.840
We don't know exactly what it is.

18:29.840 --> 18:31.840
Is it a temple?

18:31.840 --> 18:34.840
Is it an astronomical observatory?

18:34.840 --> 18:39.840
Is it from the times of Merlin and King Arthur?

18:39.840 --> 18:42.840
Stonehenge fact file.

18:42.840 --> 18:44.840
Where?

18:44.840 --> 18:49.840
It is near Salisbury in the south of England.

18:49.840 --> 18:51.840
When?

18:51.840 --> 18:56.840
No one knows exactly, but there are three construction periods.

18:56.840 --> 18:58.840
One.

18:58.840 --> 19:07.840
In 3000 BC, there is a circular ditch with a diameter of around 100 meters.

19:07.840 --> 19:09.840
Two.

19:09.840 --> 19:16.840
In 2500 BC, there is the original monument.

19:16.840 --> 19:19.840
It is made of wood.

19:19.840 --> 19:20.840
Three.

19:20.840 --> 19:26.840
Between 2500 and 1500 BC,

19:26.840 --> 19:30.840
people build the stone monument.

19:30.840 --> 19:32.840
Who?

19:32.840 --> 19:35.840
There are lots of interesting theories.

19:35.840 --> 19:36.840
Druids.

19:36.840 --> 19:38.840
People from Atlantis.

19:38.840 --> 19:40.840
Merlin the Magician.

19:40.840 --> 19:41.840
Aliens.

19:41.840 --> 19:47.840
Probably primitive British people are the architects.

19:47.840 --> 19:49.840
Why?

19:49.840 --> 19:53.840
No one knows, but here are some ideas.

19:54.840 --> 19:58.840
Perhaps people use Stonehenge to study the sky.

19:58.840 --> 20:04.840
They want to see the changes in the sun, the moon and the stars.

20:04.840 --> 20:10.840
With this information, they can understand the seasons and the weather.

20:10.840 --> 20:19.840
Perhaps Stonehenge is an enormous calendar, an observatory or a computer.

20:19.840 --> 20:28.840
Perhaps it is a magic temple to an ancient god or the tomb of an important king.

20:28.840 --> 20:31.840
How?

20:31.840 --> 20:34.840
This is a mystery too.

20:34.840 --> 20:40.840
The stones are very big and they are very heavy.

20:40.840 --> 20:43.840
Some stones are blue stones.

20:43.840 --> 20:51.840
From the Priscilla Mountains in South Wales, 385 kilometers away.

20:51.840 --> 20:55.840
No one knows how the people moved them.

20:56.840 --> 20:58.840
Chapter 6.

20:58.840 --> 21:01.840
Ashik.

